title: Ep 30: Isolation
description: One of my favorite Joy Division songs and also a part of human existence. The Duggars are a result of isolation and I want to take credit for hating them way before anyone else did. In this episode I discuss social and emotional isolation.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
